{"author":"RebarBotNava","data":{"body":"[E3] Workflow PR-event audit — no breakage. grep -l pull_request .github/workflows/* => eval-plan-review-container.yml, eval.yml, optionality.yml, test.yml. All trigger on plain 'pull_request:' (not pull_request_target). A bot-closed fork PR may cancel these runs early, which is acceptable (a fork PR cannot merge here regardless). None are broken by the lockdown bot; the new lockdown.yml uses a distinct pull_request_target event and scopes permissions to pull-requests:write only, so it does not interfere. No fix or discovered_from ticket needed."},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"COMMENT","timestamp":1783649307382398001,"uuid":"d4c9d4cb-3e24-4d44-ad91-b6be3620bcf5"}